      "text": "（さーて……どう答えたもんかなぁ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseent-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 5.4592062633
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃんは、事務所では楽しそうにやってますよ\nリズノワとか、他の先輩達にも凄く可愛がられてますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……それでもやっぱり、親御さんは心配ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7258730253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseent-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.3858728727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、こころちゃんは、リズノワのメンバーとして\nBIG4っていう、アイドルのトップに立った訳です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "日本にこれだけアイドルがいる中で\nそれはやっぱり、凄いことなんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseent-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.5169160207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "だからこころちゃんは、まだ子供ではありますけど\n立派なアイドルなので、そこは信頼してあげて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんkanaも、こころちゃんが困っている時は\nいつでも助けますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseent-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 44.9249897639
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　あいつ……\nまぁいいか、今はほっとこ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseent-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 50.9528127829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、今日は撮影にご協力ありがとうございました\nそれじゃ、また遊びに来させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――公開収録前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4828798453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.6828798453
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.6828798453
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.7695466519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "んー……そろそろスタジオ入りだな\nほら、いつまでもぐだぐだスマホ弄ってんなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9333335876,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4500,
          "startTime": 70.4333335876
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7266.66666669999,
          "startTime": 73.2000002543
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.7653289955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "分かってますよぉ\n……あ、お母さんからメッセだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5666669209,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2568.004592099996,
          "startTime": 72.3333335876
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5099.999745799991,
          "startTime": 77.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.0055105051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "今日の収録を観に来るとは言ってたんですけど\nお父さんも休み取れたから、二人で来てるみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.3715649765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "ほー。誘ったら翌週にはいそいそ観に来るんだから\nあんたの親、つくづく強火担だねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.70541962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。この前、母親とkanaが玄関で話してるの\nあんた、こそこそ盗み聞きしてたでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.6310204985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ……まさかkanaさんが、こころのことを\nあんなに高く買ってくれてるとは、思わなかったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.3840589685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ここは邪魔しちゃ悪いなって思って\n感動して、聞き入っちゃってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、まだまだ言い足りないですよね～？\nほらほら、心ゆくまでこころを褒めていいんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.8610657218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "ガキが、調子に乗るなっつの\n……そういやイジメのこと、なんで言わなかったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.6800227328
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "あんたんとこ、いい親じゃん\nイジメのことだって、ちゃんと話聞いてくれただろうに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.3653515342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "ただでさえアイドルやるのを応援してもらってるのに\nこれ以上、心配なんか掛けられませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2437558658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……いい親ならいい親で\n悩むことがあるもんだなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.4321766857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、うちのお父さんが本気になったら\n学校の先生も教育委員会も、一網打尽になっちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "毎度毎度、ガキが一丁前に気を遣いやがって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4788434669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.4788434669
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.1498640224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "でもガキの浅知恵なんざ、どうせ大人にはバレてっから\n隠し事も、ほどほどにしときな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
