    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "さーて……じゃ、一仕事してくるかぁ\n親に心配掛けたくないなら、本番で絶対失敗すんなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.6000063578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.6000063578
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.4685544972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "分かってますよ～だ。kanaさんこそ\n仲良しアピール忘れないで下さいよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.1666730244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.4666712443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "――はい、と言う訳で\nこころの実家ロケの様子を、お送りしました～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.0666730244,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3824.927011699998,
          "startTime": 197.3999984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "この取材、すっごく楽しかったんだけど\nカトちゃんを撫でられなかったのが心残りでさぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.6000063578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ～、こころちゃん\n今度、カトちゃん、事務所に連れて来てよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.2666730244,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 207.5612170224
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "ちっちゃいこころの写真じゃなくて\nそっちが気になってるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.6666730244,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3352.1223063000034,
          "startTime": 215.7333396911
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば撮影の後に、お母さんに\n「kanaちゃんってどんな感じ？」って聞かれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.2333287556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "お。なんて答えたの？　どきどき",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.2692868077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも相談に乗ってくれて、励ましてくれる\nお姉ちゃんみたいに頼りになる人だって答えといたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.266662089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "（性格悪いし、正直大人としてどうかと思うけど）\n（たまに頼りになるのは……まぁ、嘘じゃないし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.8666699726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan022.m4a",
      "text": "ほんと～？　本当にそう思ってくれてる？\nkanaも、こころちゃんは妹みたいに大事だよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.0999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kan024.m4a",
      "text": "（面倒くさいクソガキだけど、下手な気の遣い方して）\n（意地張ろうとするとこは、嫌いじゃない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.7666699726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_10_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "さ～て！　それでは、公開収録の特別企画\nスタジオから、ミニライブをお届けします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.9000094095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
